			&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;
			Select &lt;b&gt;Plot&lt;/b&gt; to access data via ADDE
			&lt;li&gt;
			&lt;b&gt;Sounding&lt;/b&gt; data can be local or remote
			&lt;li&gt;
			Select &lt;b&gt;Wind Profiler&lt;/b&gt; to access data via ADDE
			&lt;/ul&gt;
		" />
	</panel>

